#. Tag: title
#: help.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid "Help &krusader;"
msgstr "Pomoč &krusader;"

#. Tag: primary
#: help.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid "Help"
msgstr "Pomoč"

#. Tag: para
#: help.docbook:12
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here is your opportunity to <ulink url=\"https://krusader.org/get-involved/"
"index.html\">contribute</ulink> to the &krusader; project. There are things "
"that need to be done, but cannot be done by us. If you feel you can help, do "
"not hesitate to contact us; every OpenSource can use some help. Please also "
"check the <ulink url=\"https://krusader.org/get-involved/index.html"
"\">contribute</ulink> donate &URL; page on our website for more recent "
"information. Thanks!"
msgstr ""
"Tukaj je vaša priložnost, da <ulink url=\"https://krusader.org/get-involved/"
"index.html\">prispevate</ulink> k &krusader; projekt. Obstajajo stvari, ki "
"jih je treba narediti, a jih ne moremo storiti sami. Če menite, da lahko "
"pomagate, ne oklevajte in nas kontaktirajte; vsak OpenSource lahko potrebuje "
"pomoč. Preverite tudi <ulink url=\"https://krusader.org/get-involved/index."
"html\">prispevajte</ulink> donirajte &URL; strani na naši spletni strani za "
"novejše informacije. hvala!"

#. Tag: para
#: help.docbook:18
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To get contributor account and commit changes to &krusader; by yourselves "
"you should follow <ulink url=\"https://community.kde.org/Infrastructure/"
"Get_a_Developer_Account\">this tutorial</ulink>. Some useful advice on using "
"&kde; Git can be found <ulink url=\"https://community.kde.org/Infrastructure/"
"Git\">here</ulink>. It is a good practice to use <ulink url=\"https://invent."
"kde.org/utilities/krusader/-/merge_requests\">merge requests</ulink> for the "
"non-trivial patches."
msgstr ""
"Če želite pridobiti račun sodelavca in izvesti spremembe v &krusader; sami, "
"bi morali slediti <ulink url=\"https://community.kde.org/Infrastructure/"
"Get_a_Developer_Account\">tem učbeniku</ulink>. Nekaj koristnih nasvetov o "
"uporabi &kde; Git lahko najdete <ulink url=\"https://community.kde.org/"
"Infrastructure/Git\">tukaj</ulink>. Dobra praksa je uporaba <ulink url="
"\"https://invent.kde.org/utilities/krusader/-/merge_requests\">zahtev za "
"združevanje</ulink> za netrivialne popravke."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: help.docbook:23
#, no-c-format
msgid "Documentation"
msgstr "Dokumentacija"

#. Tag: para
#: help.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Help is needed (we are looking for documentation writers) for keeping the "
"&krusader; documentation up to date. The draft explanation of new features "
"is done by the developers on the <ulink url=\"https://groups.google.com/"
"group/krusader-devel\">krusader-devel mailing list</ulink>, but we need "
"editors to add this information in the handbook. By playing with the new "
"features these editors can give valuable information to the developers for "
"making the new features even better!"
msgstr ""
"Potrebna je pomoč (iščemo pisce dokumentacije) za ohranjanje datoteke "
"&krusader; dokumentacija posodobljena. Osnutek razlage novih funkcij "
"pripravijo razvijalci na <ulink url=\"https://groups.google.com/group/"
"krusader-devel\">poštnem seznamu za krusader-devel</ulink>, vendar "
"potrebujemo urednike, dodajte te podatke v priročnik. Z igranjem z novimi "
"funkcijami lahko ti urejevalniki dajo dragocene informacije razvijalcem za "
"izboljšanje novih funkcij!"

#. Tag: emphasis
#: help.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bug triaging"
msgstr "Triažiranje napak"

#. Tag: para
#: help.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sometimes bugs are not well reported, that can be mended. In order to free "
"developers, so that they can have more time to &eg; improve &krusader;'s "
"source code and add features: bug reports can be confirmed, or closed. A "
"list of steps to repeat the problem can be made. Some potential causes can "
"be discarded."
msgstr ""
"Včasih napake niso dobro prijavljene, kar je mogoče popraviti. Da bi "
"osvobodili razvijalce, da bi imeli več časa za &eg; izboljšajte izvorno kodo "
"&krusader; in dodajte funkcije: poročila o napakah se lahko potrdijo ali "
"zaprejo. Sestavi se lahko seznam korakov za ponovitev težave. Nekatere možne "
"vzroke je mogoče zavreči."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: help.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid "Code testing"
msgstr "Testiranje kode"

#. Tag: para
#: help.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Before a new &krusader; release is made... many testers are needed to report "
"or confirm problems. If you like to be on the cutting edge of &krusader;, "
"and help by the way, consider reporting!"
msgstr ""
"Pred novim &krusader; izdaja je narejena ... potrebnih je veliko "
"preizkuševalcev za poročanje ali potrditev težav. Če želite biti na vrhuncu "
"&krusader; in mimogrede pomagati, razmislite o poročanju!"

#. Tag: emphasis
#: help.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding comments"
msgstr "Dodajanje komentarjev"

#. Tag: para
#: help.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are reading &krusader;'s source code, and you think that adding "
"comments is a good idea, that's welcome! It's very probable that your "
"comments will save time to someone else later, accelerating &krusader;'s "
"development."
msgstr ""
"Če berete izvorno kodo &krusader; in menite, da je dodajanje komentarjev "
"dobra ideja, je to dobrodošlo! Zelo verjetno je, da bodo vaši komentarji "
"kasneje nekomu prihranili čas in tako pospešili razvoj &krusader;-ja."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: help.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tutorial writing"
msgstr "Pisanje vadnic"

#. Tag: para
#: help.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Tutorials are very useful for people who are starting to use a program, like "
"&krusader;."
msgstr ""
"Vadnice so zelo uporabne za ljudi, ki začenjajo uporabljati program, kot je "
"&krusader;."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: help.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid "English texts reviewing"
msgstr "Pregled angleških besedil"

#. Tag: para
#: help.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you can review English texts, and spot writing mistakes, your comments "
"are welcome!"
msgstr ""
"Če znate pregledovati angleška besedila in opaziti pisne napake, so vaši "
"komentarji dobrodošli!"

#. Tag: emphasis
#: help.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid "Solve doubts about &krusader;"
msgstr "Rešite dvome glede &krusader;"

#. Tag: para
#: help.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some &krusader; users can write about their doubts, &eg; in mailing lists. "
"Solving their doubts is very valuable!"
msgstr ""
"Nekateri &krusader; uporabniki lahko pišejo o svojih dvomih, &eg; na poštnih "
"seznamih. Reševanje njihovih dvomov je zelo dragoceno!"

#. Tag: emphasis
#: help.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid "&krusader; Extensions"
msgstr "&krusader; Razširitve"

#. Tag: para
#: help.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please upload your favourite extensions at <ulink url=\"https://store.kde."
"org/\">store.kde.org</ulink>, so that they become available for the "
"&krusader; community. Maybe they will be shipped by default with &krusader; "
"at the next release :-))."
msgstr ""
"Naložite svoje priljubljene razširitve na <ulink url=\"https://store.kde.org/"
"\">store.kde.org</ulink>, da bodo na voljo za &krusader; skupnosti. Morda "
"bodo privzeto poslani z &krusader; ob naslednji objavi :-))."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: help.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid "Spread the Word &krusader;"
msgstr "Razširite besedo &krusader;"

#. Tag: para
#: help.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you like &krusader;, let people know! Write articles and reviews for "
"internet or print publications. Encourage your friends to give &krusader; a "
"try. Participate in forums to help others in the community."
msgstr ""
"Če vam je všeč &krusader;, povejte ljudem! Pišite članke in ocene za "
"internetne ali tiskane publikacije. Spodbudite svoje prijatelje, da "
"&krusader; poskusiti. Sodelujte na forumih in pomagajte drugim v skupnosti."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: help.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid "&GUI; Translations"
msgstr "&GUI; Prevodi"

#. Tag: para
#: help.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&krusader; is available in many languages, but sometimes translations do "
"need an update or translations to new languages are always welcome. If you "
"are interested in translating the &krusader; &GUI;, please contact the "
"<ulink url=\"https://l10n.kde.org/teams-list.php\">&kde; translation team</"
"ulink> of your language."
msgstr ""
"&krusader; je na voljo v številnih jezikih, včasih pa je treba prevode "
"posodobiti ali pa so prevodi v nove jezike vedno dobrodošli. Če vas zanima "
"prevod &krusader; &GUI;, se obrnite na <ulink url=\"https://l10n.kde.org/"
"teams-list.php\">&kde; prevajalska ekipa</ulink> vašega jezika."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: help.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid "Documentation Translations"
msgstr "Prevodi dokumentacije"

#. Tag: para
#: help.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are interested in translating this &krusader; documentation, please "
"contact the <ulink url=\"https://l10n.kde.org/teams-list.php\">&kde; "
"translation team</ulink> of your language."
msgstr ""
"Če vas zanima prevod tega &krusader; dokumentacijo, se obrnite na <ulink url="
"\"https://l10n.kde.org/teams-list.php\">&kde; prevajalska ekipa</ulink> "
"vašega jezika."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: help.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid "Donations"
msgstr "Donacije"

#. Tag: para
#: help.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Actually, we had not considered donations, until users asked us for a way to "
"<ulink url=\"https://sourceforge.net/project/project_donations.php?"
"group_id=6488\">Donate</ulink> to the project. &krusader; is, and always "
"will be free, in all the terms of the GNU Public License."
msgstr ""
"Pravzaprav nismo upoštevali donacij, dokler nas uporabniki niso vprašali za "
"način <ulink url=\"https://sourceforge.net/project/project_donations.php?"
"group_id=6488\">Donacije</ulink> za projekt. &krusader; je in bo vedno "
"brezplačen v vseh pogojih javne licence GNU."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: help.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid "Packagers"
msgstr "Pakirnice"

#. Tag: para
#: help.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"We are always in need of packagers for different distro rpm's, deb's, &etc; "
"All help is welcome."
msgstr ""
"Vedno potrebujemo pakirnike za različne distribucijske vrtljaje, deb &etc; "
"Vsaka pomoč je dobrodošla."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: help.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid "<emphasis>FAQ</emphasis>"
msgstr "<emphasis>FAQ</emphasis>"

#. Tag: para
#: help.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have a question that is missing in the <link linkend=\"faq\">FAQ</"
"link>, we would like to hear it."
msgstr ""
"Če imate vprašanje, ki manjka v <link linkend=\"faq\">pogostih vprašanjih</"
"link>, ga želimo slišati."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: help.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rate &krusader;"
msgstr "Ocenite &krusader;"

#. Tag: para
#: help.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On some websites you can rate software, if you like &krusader; go to one of "
"these sites and rate &krusader;, thanks."
msgstr ""
"Na nekaterih spletnih mestih lahko ocenite programsko opremo, če vam je všeč "
"&krusader; pojdite na eno od teh mest in ocenite &krusader;, hvala."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: help.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid "Others"
msgstr "Drugo"

#. Tag: para
#: help.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"faqg_wish\">Feedback</link>, <link linkend=\"faqg_bug_report"
"\">Bug reports</link>, patches, &etc; are always welcome! An open source "
"project's greatest strength is derived from getting user feedback."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"faqg_wish\">Povratne informacije</link>, <link linkend="
"\"faqg_bug_report\">Poročila o napakah</link>, popravki &etc; vedno "
"dobrodošli! Največja moč odprtokodnega projekta izhaja iz pridobivanja "
"povratnih informacij uporabnikov."
